697
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:34,799
You can do many interesting things alone.

698
00:34:36,160 --> 00:34:37,680
I really enjoy going out alone.

699
00:34:37,680 --> 00:34:39,440
Traveling solo.

700
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:41,839
Every trip feels like an adventure.

701
00:34:41,839 --> 00:34:43,200
That's the feeling.

702
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,640
I often go out alone too.

703
00:34:45,640 --> 00:34:47,279
I feel like only when I'm alone...

704
00:34:47,279 --> 00:34:48,960
can I truly...

705
00:34:51,479 --> 00:34:53,239
experience certain things.

706
00:34:53,239 --> 00:34:53,960
Very free.

707
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:56,120
Anyway, I feel very free when alone.

708
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:58,479
Yes, exactly.

709
00:34:58,479 --> 00:35:01,400
And as I grow older...

710
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:04,279
the more I prefer being alone.

711
00:35:04,279 --> 00:35:06,039
This is just human...

712
00:35:06,039 --> 00:35:07,039
normal...

713
00:35:07,039 --> 00:35:07,799
perfectly normal...

714
00:35:07,799 --> 00:35:10,120
part of the aging process.

715
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:14,759
Spending this day with Fujie...

716
00:35:14,759 --> 00:35:16,680
I discovered many...

717
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:19,600
other charms beneath his surface.

718
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:20,999
A day with him...

719
00:35:20,999 --> 00:35:22,999
made me feel that...

720
00:35:22,999 --> 00:35:25,839
there's something very attractive about his inner self.

721
00:35:25,839 --> 00:35:27,319
It makes me want to know him better.

722
00:35:32,239 --> 00:35:33,640
I'll have a chicken wing.

723
00:35:33,640 --> 00:35:34,400
These are chicken feet.

724
00:35:35,319 --> 00:35:36,360
There are still two pieces of meat left, aren't there?

725
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,999
I don't eat that, it's too fatty.

726
00:35:39,799 --> 00:35:41,319
You should rinse it first before eating.

727
00:35:41,319 --> 00:35:42,239
I need to soak up some oil.

728
00:35:43,039 --> 00:35:45,200
This is how I usually eat when dining out.

729
00:35:45,200 --> 00:35:46,680
You're so strict with yourself.

730
00:35:46,680 --> 00:35:48,360
Yes, for decades.

731
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:49,799
Years have passed like a single day.

732
00:35:49,799 --> 00:35:51,400
Then I eat river snail noodles every day.

733
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:52,960
So stinky.

734
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:53,839
So fragrant.

735
00:35:53,839 --> 00:35:55,680
I've never tried it, not once in my life.

736
00:35:56,600 --> 00:35:58,799
Extremely fragrant.

737
00:35:58,799 --> 00:36:00,360
Then I can use it to stink up your place.

738
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,039
I've never had it.

739
00:36:02,279 --> 00:36:04,200
Didn't someone bring river snail noodles?

740
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:05,039
Can we ask them to make it?

741
00:36:05,039 --> 00:36:07,239
After making it, we'll leave it in your room overnight.

742
00:36:07,239 --> 00:36:08,960
How much perfume would we need

743
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:09,880
to cover up that smell?

744
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:11,200
Actually, I brought perfume.

745
00:36:11,200 --> 00:36:12,120
I brought two bottles.

746
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:13,440
What perfume did you bring?

747
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:15,200
Let me see what your taste is like.

748
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:19,600
My favorite perfume.

749
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:20,559
It smells wonderful.

750
00:36:20,559 --> 00:36:21,720
That shows that you

751
00:36:21,720 --> 00:36:24,360
prefer a certain type of everyday feeling.

752
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:25,680
I'm very

753
00:36:25,680 --> 00:36:26,160
Very what?

754
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:26,920
Stylish, very stylish.

755
00:36:28,079 --> 00:36:29,920
Someone said I have style, I'm very stylish.

756
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:30,880
When I sleep at night,

757
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,640
I must light aromatherapy and listen to soft music.

758
00:36:33,160 --> 00:36:34,239
Then have a glass of red wine before bed.

759
00:36:37,039 --> 00:36:38,440
That made me laugh.

760
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,039
What's so funny?

761
00:36:39,039 --> 00:36:40,319
Wouldn't have guessed.

762
00:36:40,319 --> 00:36:41,759
Bro, you're amazing.

763
00:36:41,759 --> 00:36:42,920
Thank you.

764
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,360
Fang Xu is very enthusiastic.

765
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,799
He's on the same wavelength as me.

766
00:36:45,799 --> 00:36:47,039
When we talk,

767
00:36:47,039 --> 00:36:49,279
we just understand each other.

768
00:36:49,279 --> 00:36:50,880
Of course, I do have some affection for him.

769
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:53,960
It depends on whether

770
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:56,239
this affection can develop into something deeper.

771
00:37:09,519 --> 00:37:10,839
This tofu is pretty good.

772
00:37:10,839 --> 00:37:11,559
Really?

773
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:14,880
That's because I was the one who served it to you.

774
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:20,120
I genuinely haven't eaten anything this...

775
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:21,880
delicious in a long time.

776
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:24,400
What we had for lunch yesterday was similar.

777
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,920
I didn't get to eat yesterday because...

778
00:37:25,920 --> 00:37:26,360
it was too far.

779
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:26,960
Too much distance.

780
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:30,680
I want some iced cola.

781
00:37:30,680 --> 00:37:32,440
We had some yesterday.

782
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:33,600
I know.

783
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:35,759
If we complete any missions successfully today,

784
00:37:35,759 --> 00:37:36,640
let's get some more.

785
00:37:36,640 --> 00:37:37,799
Mhm.

786
00:37:37,799 --> 00:37:40,200
I saw in their supply room...

787
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:42,759
there's a wine set,

788
00:37:42,759 --> 00:37:43,600
but no actual wine.

789
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:44,640
Right.

790
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:47,759
We can just hold the glasses and pretend.

791
00:37:47,759 --> 00:37:50,360
We could use them for iced cola!

792
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:54,200
We still have ice cubes.

793
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:55,640
Then we'll wear our fanciest clothes,

794
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:58,680
carry the glasses around on patrol,

795
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:01,279
and toast everyone.

796
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:04,039
He Jinyi...

797
00:38:04,039 --> 00:38:07,200
I hope we can take things slower.

798
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:08,640
Because I think...

799
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:11,160
we've been moving too fast these days.

800
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:13,279
Our relationship progressed too quickly.

801
00:38:13,279 --> 00:38:16,839
I hope we can take more time to understand each other

802
00:38:16,839 --> 00:38:20,200
before making any decisions.

803
00:38:26,799 --> 00:38:29,839
The Survival Arena will open in the afternoon

804
00:38:29,839 --> 00:38:32,239
All islanders, please be prepared

805
00:38:40,319 --> 00:38:41,400
Hello

806
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:42,279
Come in

807
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:53,559
I'm going on a date with a guy.

808
00:38:55,279 --> 00:38:56,479
Guess who it is.

809
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,440
Fu Jie.

810
00:39:01,279 --> 00:39:02,680
For several days in a row,

811
00:39:02,680 --> 00:39:03,720
