812
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:05,640
But when it came to deciding your fate,

813
00:39:05,640 --> 00:39:06,640
he didn't choose you.

814
00:39:06,640 --> 00:39:07,600
Would you still go after him?

815
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:09,360
You mean Fu Jie?

816
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,400
Right, I don't want to do that anymore.

817
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,360
I think it's pointless.

818
00:39:14,839 --> 00:39:16,720
Then you should ask Gu Zhenxiang out.

819
00:39:16,720 --> 00:39:17,880
Right, I'll ask Gu Zhenxiang.

820
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:19,319
Gu Zhenxiang.

821
00:39:19,319 --> 00:39:20,839
The reason I'm asking Gu Zhenxiang is because

822
00:39:20,839 --> 00:39:24,079
on the first day's event, we were in the same team.

823
00:39:24,079 --> 00:39:25,360
And he's very gentlemanly,

824
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:26,999
he takes good care of girls.

825
00:39:26,999 --> 00:39:27,519
Yes, he's quite good.

826
00:39:27,519 --> 00:39:28,239
So I think he's pretty nice.

827
00:39:28,239 --> 00:39:29,680
And he's not the kind of person

828
00:39:29,680 --> 00:39:30,519
who's boring.

829
00:39:30,519 --> 00:39:31,680
With some people, when you chat with them,

830
00:39:31,680 --> 00:39:33,880
if the conversation doesn't flow, it feels exhausting.

831
00:39:33,880 --> 00:39:35,160
Right.

832
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:36,200
Yes.

833
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:37,600
Gu Zhenxiang is alright too.

834
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:39,039
Gu Zhenxiang is currently

835
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,839
completely infatuated with Hu Wei.

836
00:39:46,640 --> 00:39:48,440
You know they're taking turns

837
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:51,120
two guys accompanying Hu Wei every day.

838
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,680
Divine map

839
00:39:59,680 --> 00:40:00,720
Looks good

840
00:40:00,720 --> 00:40:02,239
Won't show you

841
00:40:02,239 --> 00:40:03,920
Just one glance

842
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:04,680
Got it

843
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:05,960
From this angle

844
00:40:06,440 --> 00:40:07,799
Starting to act

845
00:40:07,799 --> 00:40:08,440
Quite nice

846
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:09,519
I took a really good shot

847
00:40:09,519 --> 00:40:10,200
Let me see it

848
00:40:10,200 --> 00:40:11,680
Just a second, a quick glimpse

849
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:16,680
Want some iced Americano?

850
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:17,600
Still has ice cubes

851
00:40:19,039 --> 00:40:20,680
Only this much for now

852
00:40:24,759 --> 00:40:25,839
I was gonna say

853
00:40:25,839 --> 00:40:28,960
How does it feel sharing a tent with Gu Zhenxiang?

854
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:29,759
Asking me?

855
00:40:31,079 --> 00:40:32,640
Your question is tricky

856
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:34,160
All I can say is

857
00:40:34,160 --> 00:40:35,680
The dynamic is... delicate

858
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:48,079
Look

859
00:40:48,079 --> 00:40:49,279
The sunscreen is exactly the same

